Huawei is offering great savings on a variety of its consumer tech products this Black Friday. These include great deals on smartphones, smart watches, tablets, and earbuds. You can nab Huawei’s FreeBuds for just R999 – save R1,000 – as well as the Huawei Watch 2, which is available for half price at R1,999. Huawei will also be offering great value on mid-range smartphones such as the P smart 2019 and Y7 2019 – offering savings of R1,000 and R1,500 respectively. Terms and conditions apply, and stocks are limited – so make sure to make your purchases early to avoid disappointment. View Huawei’s awesome Black Friday deals below. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-329831" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-640x217.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="217" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-640x217.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-600x203.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-768x260.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-1536x520.jpg 1536w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___-1200x406.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday4___.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-329829" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday3__-640x217.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="217" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday3__-640x217.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday3__-600x203.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/BlackFriday3__-768x260.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/